{"tid":2080591,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"光復連登 由Admin做起","createTime":"2020-06-26T13:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T00:49:15.000Z","uid":112846,"like":24,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9bb1fb42d83169cd5aaed162546083466a5bfb73","tid":2080591,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"自從反送中惡法開始，連登成為行動、文宣既意見交流集中地，亦都係度吹到唔少雞去搞眾籌同聯署，一時間呢個forum變左成個世界都關注同研究既重心。<br />\n<br />\n但因為咁，連登就引黎唔少藍蛆、曱甴係度搧風點火，鬥黃、鬥乜鬥盛，好多行動post都係推唔郁，同埋引發好多不必然既內鬥。<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望連尼住可以考慮以下幾個建議：<br />\n1.將2019年會6月或之前既account全部ban曬，因為我相信班藍蛆曱甴仲未滲透連登，係呢場己亥革命前，佢地係連登既影響力唔高<br />\n<br />\n2.對於有五毛係6月前就開左account，果d要ban埋<br />\n<br />\n3.參考台灣ptt做法，係約干期限內禁止開新account<br />\n<br />\n4.直接將行動post置頂同分係熱門<br />\n<br />\n5.設立上訴機制，如果有重要user係19年6月後先開account，可以透過上訴機制去解封account<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望連登變番一個有行動力同影響力既forum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b487b27bb3533a27cb3b423fea1f83844acaaf0","tid":2080591,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:59:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"83b869f3bd7bda041c62e2c127910cac5a41f81d","tid":2080591,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:59:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c20352aa7d02e473162685c8a6fe1b43ef8c7e6f","tid":2080591,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:59:24.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"27fc50242179c1ebb4e39285a7195e9aff6f0b72","tid":2080591,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"78c3e68e24d4a7496fe7e2be59cb2a2ed44f1450","tid":2080591,"uid":112846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T13:59:45.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"cabe0ba422bfb262